**Action:** Validate Assumptions Against the Codebase

**Please provide the context:**

- **The System/Feature to Validate:** [e.g., "The user authentication system," "The invoicing module."]

- **Assumptions to Validate (one per line):**
  - [e.g., The system uses JWT for session management.]
  - [e.g., All database queries are handled through an ORM.]
  - [e.g., An invoice can only be deleted by the user who created it.]

**Instruction for the AI:**
For each assumption listed, analyze the codebase to determine if it is **Confirmed** or **Inaccurate**. If an assumption is inaccurate, please explain the actual implementation and cite the relevant file(s) and line number(s) as evidence.
